@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zidzcw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v0 + wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.29)))
    v1 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.97 * v0 + 0.99) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.10)))
    v1 = 0.00
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(v2))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.89 / v1 + 0.35)) - 0.66)
    tmp = ((v2 * (v1 + 0.49 / v0 + 0.97)) - wp.sin(v2))
    v0 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.59 * tmp + 0.98)) / wp.exp(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
